text: Raymond Uytterhaeghe (born 25 October 1947) is a French wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:French male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of France Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nord (French department)
